, . , . , , Kaggle https://www.kaggle.com/c/bike-sharing-demand/data, ( . hour.csv DatasetDescription.txt) - UCI Machine Learning Repository https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Bike+Sharing+Dataset

, , Kaggle https://www.kaggle.com/c/bike-sharing-demand. , Root Mean Squared Logarithmic Error (RMSLE)

2011 2012 . Capital Bikeshare system, Washington D.C., USA

  • datetime - hourly date + timestamp
  • season - 1 = spring, 2 = summer, 3 = fall, 4 = winter
  • holiday - whether the day is considered a holiday
  • workingday - whether the day is neither a weekend nor holiday

  • weather

    1: Clear, Few clouds, Partly cloudy, Partly cloudy 2: Mist + Cloudy, Mist + Broken clouds, Mist + Few clouds, Mist 3: Light Snow, Light Rain + Thunderstorm + Scattered clouds, Light Rain + Scattered clouds 4: Heavy Rain + Ice Pallets + Thunderstorm + Mist, Snow + Fog
  • temp - temperature in Celsius
  • atemp - feels like temperature in Celsius
  • humidity - relative humidity
  • windspeed - wind speed
  • casual - number of non-registered user rentals initiated
  • registered - number of registered user rentals initiated

  • count - number of total rentals
